g.text: And you're looking for a skilled one, who has a
positive attitude and is fun to work with.
You want a proactive, pragmatic dev pal with
the right amount of grit for your business.
But… it's hard to ﬁnd the right one.
Well… I was waiting for you;)
Converted into a frontend enthusiast dev,
writing code and moving pixels in the www.
I'm ready to merge with your team; bringing
the very best of myself to reach our goals of
Let’s put our heads together to solve this.
